{"tid":2353943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"愛丁堡動物園沒錢了 熊貓陽光和甜甜明年或被迫回國","createTime":"2021-01-05T06:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T07:41:46.000Z","uid":225931,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"aae3f47e8de6398c0532b6daeb45475642840e93","tid":2353943,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:22:50.000Z","msg":"由於經濟壓力，蘇格蘭愛丁堡動物園的大熊貓明年可能不得不返回中國。<br />\n<br />\n這裏的兩隻大熊貓「陽光」和「甜甜」來自中國，它們的租賃費用約為每年100萬英鎊。<br />\n<br />\n該動物園希望繼續養育這對大熊貓，但園方與中國政府簽訂的10年合同即將到期，可能無法再續約。<br />\n<br />\n新冠疫情帶來的封鎖導致蘇格蘭皇家動物學會（Royal Zoological Society of Scotland）的損失高達200萬英鎊，該學會負責愛丁堡動物園（Edinburgh Zoo）和高地野生動物公園（Highland Wildlife Park）的運營。<br />\n<br />\nADVERTISEMENT<br />\n<br />\n學會總裁大衛&middot;菲爾德（David Field）表示，慈善機構將不得不「認真考慮每一項潛在的節約措施」，包括大熊貓的合同。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，因防疫而閉園對這家慈善機構帶來了「巨大的財務影響」，因為它的大部分收入來自遊客。<br />\n<br />\n「儘管我們的公園重新開放了，但去年我們損失了約200萬英鎊。幾乎可以肯定的是，出行限制、社交距離和對遊客數量的限制將持續一段時間，這也將減少我們的收入，」菲爾德說。"},{"pid":"c936e1a8fff5b0f381f32b983ea75015ce62ef38","tid":2353943,"uid":335434,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:25:56.000Z","msg":"每年用成千萬同支国租隻連仆嘢都唔願郁嘅大食懶返嚟養 鬼佬錢真係好易呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c317bbe649b90648c8a8e964ecfa06969b079c9c","tid":2353943,"uid":387466,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:27:18.000Z","msg":"返去食支竹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3315892bff63cfa97338d9df1ae22a5b8419123f","tid":2353943,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:28:29.000Z","msg":"最慘係有隻美國出世嘅熊貓都要被中國籍"},{"pid":"10487179e4ec95182effb1224c7156339636b2cb","tid":2353943,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:28:53.000Z","msg":"走得好"},{"pid":"beb25a9fb4c71f5123f8bfd65455a0814a6c4982","tid":2353943,"uid":65328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:29:52.000Z","msg":"個個國家都唔養， 支那就少一大筆外匯"},{"pid":"c173670e3086ebec4bda13c24999226928829cef","tid":2353943,"uid":19437,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:30:58.000Z","msg":"屌，我唔想返支那。"},{"pid":"1376bee003096bf47e999c9278b138cd1a62a755","tid":2353943,"uid":69544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:35:23.000Z","msg":"熊貓究竟有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9234c39ed003633fb38512a5a84479287cc00414","tid":2353943,"uid":128741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:36:14.000Z","msg":"兩個演員終於唔駛再扮熊貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3bc0a2c812a6f07ae8a8cee64079479c497d263","tid":2353943,"uid":199771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:37:34.000Z","msg":"回中國避疫"},{"pid":"b6c82b38b948fe8eb0b2cc9973141bbec4a78db4","tid":2353943,"uid":8918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9234c39ed003633fb38512a5a84479287cc00414","tid":2353943,"uid":128741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:36:14.000Z","msg":"兩個演員終於唔駛再扮熊貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:40:31.000Z","msg":"失業了"},{"pid":"be80a8f0fdeb21108bbe22d70649b679084566b4","tid":2353943,"uid":27038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1376bee003096bf47e999c9278b138cd1a62a755","tid":2353943,"uid":69544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:35:23.000Z","msg":"熊貓究竟有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:53:05.000Z","msg":"損耗別國財力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551fe1f9ea9d095d12c3fe90ccbed1d83e6f0196","tid":2353943,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:54:00.000Z","msg":"屌，我唔想返支那呀"},{"pid":"297003ed67f5479061320320e16